Global Industrial Equipment Cleaning Services Market Insights
Industrial Equipment Cleaning Services Market size was valued at USD 6.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Industrial Equipment Cleaning Services Market Overview
The industrial equipment cleaning services market is valued at USD 15.8 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 22.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% during the forecast period. The increasing demand for effective and environmentally friendly cleaning solutions, along with stringent government regulations for maintaining equipment hygiene and safety standards, are key factors driving the market. As industries across manufacturing, construction, and food processing grow, so does the need for efficient cleaning of industrial equipment to ensure optimal functioning and extend equipment life. The market is highly competitive, with several players offering specialized services across various industries.

